A simple project using autotools. 

Basic steps are these:
1 - Clone this repo.
2 - The following files are needed before we start
	src/hello.c
	src/Makefile.am
	configure.ac
	Makefile.am
	README
	AUTHORS
	ChangeLog
	NEWS
	COPYING
	autogen.sh
3 - Run $ autogen.sh
4 - Run $ ./configure
5 - Run $ make
6 - To install run $ make install
7 - To package for distribution run $ make dist
 

